basicImpl.model.generators

Class KoscielnyProduct

  • java.lang.Object
    • basicImpl.model.generators.AbstractSimpleGenerator
      • basicImpl.model.generators.KoscielnyProduct
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IRandomLatinSquareGenerator, IRandomStructureGenerator

    public class KoscielnyProduct
extends AbstractSimpleGenerator
    This class implements a generator based in the concept of product by Koscielny of two smaller LSs. The product of a LS of order n by a LS of order m returns a LS of order (n*m). This fact is used by the generator, two speed the generation of a larger LS. The results are not uniformly distributed, but the method operates in order n^2 (very fast).
    Author:
    Ignacio Gallego Sagastume
